            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1278630920,
            "creation_date": 1278630920,
            "body": "<p><code>javac<\/code> has a -target option that allows you to compile to a 1.5 jvm with a 1.6 compiler.  See <code>javac -help<\/code> for details.<\/p>\n",
